00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,968
A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES:
METEOR GARDEN

2
00:00:02,079 --> 00:00:04,999
EPISODE 33

3
00:00:05,559 --> 00:00:07,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Give up on Shancai, understand?</b></font>

4
00:00:07,279 --> 00:00:10,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Oh, all right.
-What do you mean, "Oh, all right"?</b></font>

5
00:00:10,279 --> 00:00:11,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What exactly...</b></font>

6
00:00:14,719 --> 00:00:17,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-What did you say again?
-I said all right.</b></font>

7
00:00:17,519 --> 00:00:18,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll give up on Shancai.</b></font>

8
00:00:20,839 --> 00:00:21,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why?</b></font>

9
00:00:23,719 --> 00:00:26,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-So I can pursue Shancai?
-No.</b></font>

10
00:00:32,199 --> 00:00:33,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you want to die?</b></font>

11
00:00:36,639 --> 00:00:37,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You jerk.</b></font>

12
00:00:38,519 --> 00:00:41,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I was already feeling down
but you provoked me.</b></font>

13
00:00:41,999 --> 00:00:43,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You planned all this to make me
admit my feelings.</b></font>

14
00:00:45,039 --> 00:00:46,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You think I don't know that?</b></font>

15
00:00:46,879 --> 00:00:48,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I wasn't trying to fool you.</b></font>

16
00:00:49,719 --> 00:00:51,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You even dare say that.
That's what infuriates me the most.</b></font>

17
00:00:52,639 --> 00:00:54,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But that's the most interesting part.</b></font>

18
00:00:55,039 --> 00:00:56,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Think about it.</b></font>

19
00:00:56,279 --> 00:00:59,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You knew I did it on purpose
but you still got mad.</b></font>

20
00:01:00,239 --> 00:01:01,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-That proves...
-Shut up.</b></font>

21
00:01:01,719 --> 00:01:03,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>...that your temper is really bad.</b></font>

22
00:01:04,399 --> 00:01:05,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Isn't that obvious?</b></font>

23
00:01:07,519 --> 00:01:08,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're so annoying.</b></font>

24
00:01:09,719 --> 00:01:11,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're still laughing?</b></font>

25
00:01:17,439 --> 00:01:18,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But Si.</b></font>

26
00:01:19,359 --> 00:01:23,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When have you started not doing
what you're thinking?</b></font>

27
00:01:25,639 --> 00:01:28,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even though we grew up together
and knew each other well,</b></font>

28
00:01:28,839 --> 00:01:29,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>this time,</b></font>

29
00:01:30,519 --> 00:01:32,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I was really worried that you were scared.</b></font>

30
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:37,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You don't need to worry about me.</b></font>

31
00:01:37,559 --> 00:01:39,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai's the one you should worry about.</b></font>

32
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:42,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's impossible for you not to know
what I'm thinking.</b></font>

33
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:44,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So what?</b></font>

34
00:01:44,919 --> 00:01:47,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're not saying it
so Shancai won't know either.</b></font>

35
00:01:47,759 --> 00:01:49,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I won't pass along the message anymore.</b></font>

36
00:01:53,599 --> 00:01:54,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Change your favorite slogan.</b></font>

37
00:01:55,519 --> 00:01:58,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're no longer the Lei who's not
interested in other people's business.</b></font>

38
00:02:00,279 --> 00:02:01,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai is not a stranger.</b></font>

39
00:02:02,919 --> 00:02:03,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And neither are you.</b></font>

40
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're both important to me.</b></font>

41
00:02:20,479 --> 00:02:21,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I appreciate your gesture.</b></font>

42
00:02:22,199 --> 00:02:23,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I have to remind you again.</b></font>

43
00:02:23,639 --> 00:02:25,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is all just part of your plan.</b></font>

44
00:02:26,559 --> 00:02:28,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I know, you green-eyed monster.</b></font>

45
00:02:29,279 --> 00:02:30,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you have a problem with that?</b></font>

46
00:02:32,679 --> 00:02:34,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What you're worried about won't happen.</b></font>

47
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:39,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll leave Shancai to you.</b></font>

48
00:02:40,199 --> 00:02:41,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Take good care of her.</b></font>

49
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:43,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course.</b></font>

50
00:02:45,399 --> 00:02:46,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I'm telling you.</b></font>

51
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:48,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're still my friend.</b></font>

52
00:02:49,959 --> 00:02:51,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But don't play me anymore.</b></font>

53
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:01,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The weather's so nice today.</b></font>

54
00:03:13,039 --> 00:03:14,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's time for me to go.</b></font>

55
00:03:36,119 --> 00:03:39,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lei, your parting gift is too much.</b></font>

56
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:42,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes. You fooled me so badly.</b></font>

57
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:45,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I never knew that pursuing Shancai
would have such an impact on you.</b></font>

58
00:03:46,239 --> 00:03:47,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why would it?</b></font>

59
00:03:49,279 --> 00:03:50,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But it's strange.</b></font>

60
00:03:50,879 --> 00:03:52,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You and Si had such a big fight.</b></font>

61
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:56,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I thought we couldn't be friends anymore.</b></font>

62
00:03:57,879 --> 00:04:00,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>In the end, Ximen and I
were the ones who were fooled.</b></font>

63
00:04:01,399 --> 00:04:03,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's over now.
Why are you still talking about it?</b></font>

64
00:04:04,319 --> 00:04:05,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think it was quite fun.</b></font>

65
00:04:07,279 --> 00:04:08,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're such a weirdo.</b></font>

66
00:04:13,359 --> 00:04:15,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is your family situation really bad?</b></font>

67
00:04:17,599 --> 00:04:18,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's all right.</b></font>

68
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:20,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I should go see my family anyway.</b></font>

69
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:24,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-When are you leaving?
-My flight is in the afternoon.</b></font>

70
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:25,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Be in touch.</b></font>

71
00:04:26,999 --> 00:04:28,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm already starting to miss you.</b></font>

72
00:04:29,679 --> 00:04:32,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If all goes well, I'll be back soon.
You don't have to come to the airport.</b></font>

73
00:04:36,919 --> 00:04:37,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Does Shancai know?</b></font>

74
00:04:50,879 --> 00:04:54,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Shancai, there are some things
that I couldn't tell you in person.</i></b></font>

75
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:56,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>So I sent you this voice message.</i></b></font>

76
00:04:58,039 --> 00:04:59,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>You already know right?</i></b></font>

77
00:05:00,039 --> 00:05:03,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I only wanted to make Si
face his own feelings.</i></b></font>

78
00:05:03,159 --> 00:05:04,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>That's why I decided to pursue you again.</i></b></font>

79
00:05:06,039 --> 00:05:09,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Because I can't think of any other way
to help you and Si.</i></b></font>

80
00:05:11,439 --> 00:05:14,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Sorry if it caused you any trouble.</i></b></font>

81
00:05:15,559 --> 00:05:19,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Even though it was just part of my plan,
but my concern for you is real.</i></b></font>

82
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:21,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>You know that, right?</i></b></font>

83
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:24,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I'm going back to Taiwan today.</i></b></font>

84
00:05:25,359 --> 00:05:27,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I won't be back here anytime soon.</i></b></font>

85
00:05:38,919 --> 00:05:40,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Huaze Lei!</b></font>

86
00:05:41,519 --> 00:05:46,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Goodbye!</b></font>

87
00:05:55,119 --> 00:05:57,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>When you feel like crying, do a handstand.</i></b></font>

88
00:05:57,919 --> 00:05:59,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>That way, your tears won't fall down.</i></b></font>

89
00:06:19,439 --> 00:06:20,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I'm really grateful...</i></b></font>

90
00:06:21,799 --> 00:06:23,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>to you.</i></b></font>

91
00:06:24,159 --> 00:06:25,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>You really are a nice guy.</i></b></font>

92
00:06:26,799 --> 00:06:29,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I did those things because I wanted to.</i></b></font>

93
00:06:40,999 --> 00:06:42,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Do you regret it?</i></b></font>

94
00:06:45,919 --> 00:06:46,879
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I do.</i></b></font>

95
00:06:48,039 --> 00:06:50,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I regret giving up on her so easily.</i></b></font>

96
00:06:52,119 --> 00:06:54,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I regret not holding on
a little longer that time.</i></b></font>

97
00:06:57,639 --> 00:07:00,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Shancai, do you get it?</i></b></font>

98
00:07:00,559 --> 00:07:01,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Hold on a little longer.</i></b></font>

99
00:07:02,639 --> 00:07:06,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>If you do, a lot of things
might end up differently.</i></b></font>

100
00:07:07,719 --> 00:07:09,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>But if you miss that opportunity,</i></b></font>

101
00:07:10,679 --> 00:07:12,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>you'll regret it your whole life.</i></b></font>

102
00:07:40,679 --> 00:07:42,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>QQ VOICE MESSAGE FROM HUAZE LEI</b></font>

103
00:07:47,399 --> 00:07:48,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Shancai.</i></b></font>

104
00:07:48,999 --> 00:07:52,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Knowing you was the most interesting thing
that has ever happened to me so far.</i></b></font>

105
00:07:54,119 --> 00:07:55,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>All this time,</i></b></font>

106
00:07:55,479 --> 00:07:58,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>everything we've experienced
was so beautiful.</i></b></font>

107
00:07:59,279 --> 00:08:00,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I won't ever forget it.</i></b></font>

108
00:08:01,439 --> 00:08:02,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>See you again.</i></b></font>

109
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:05,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Shancai, goodbye.</i></b></font>

110
00:08:10,359 --> 00:08:11,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Lei.</i></b></font>

111
00:08:12,359 --> 00:08:14,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Thank you for everything you did for me.</i></b></font>

112
00:08:15,479 --> 00:08:16,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Thank you.</i></b></font>

113
00:08:45,639 --> 00:08:48,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's so hard to face my own feelings.</b></font>

114
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:51,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I see.</i></b></font>

115
00:08:54,119 --> 00:08:55,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then I'll go ahead.</b></font>

116
00:09:18,359 --> 00:09:20,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I told him I'm not leaving anymore.</b></font>

117
00:09:21,479 --> 00:09:22,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He knows what I meant, right?</b></font>

118
00:09:24,519 --> 00:09:26,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then why did you get off the bus?</b></font>

119
00:09:31,079 --> 00:09:32,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did I misunderstand that?</b></font>

120
00:09:33,759 --> 00:09:35,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why did you get off the bus?</b></font>

121
00:09:44,279 --> 00:09:45,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No.</b></font>

122
00:09:46,159 --> 00:09:47,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He doesn't get it.</b></font>

123
00:09:48,159 --> 00:09:50,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He's not the type who'd care
about people's feelings.</b></font>

124
00:09:57,119 --> 00:09:59,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I really need to clearly tell him.</b></font>

125
00:10:21,039 --> 00:10:24,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Women are so annoying.</b></font>

126
00:10:27,879 --> 00:10:29,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you babbling about?</b></font>

127
00:10:31,439 --> 00:10:32,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So how are things?</b></font>

128
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:35,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did you get to see Shancai yesterday?</b></font>

129
00:10:39,759 --> 00:10:40,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yesterday...</b></font>

130
00:10:43,759 --> 00:10:45,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yesterday...</b></font>

131
00:10:55,439 --> 00:10:56,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What is he trying to say?</b></font>

132
00:10:58,279 --> 00:11:00,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think he's saying,
"Something good happened.</b></font>

133
00:11:01,559 --> 00:11:02,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He's unhappy."</b></font>

134
00:11:03,039 --> 00:11:04,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And,</b></font>

135
00:11:05,439 --> 00:11:06,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>"He doesn't understand."</b></font>

136
00:11:10,399 --> 00:11:12,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It seems Si has acquired
more depth of expression</b></font>

137
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:14,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>after going to graduate school.</b></font>

138
00:11:14,999 --> 00:11:15,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you care?</b></font>

139
00:11:16,999 --> 00:11:20,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And are you and Shancai</b></font>

140
00:11:20,919 --> 00:11:22,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>together or not?</b></font>

141
00:11:24,319 --> 00:11:25,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why do you care?</b></font>

142
00:11:26,479 --> 00:11:27,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey, Si.</b></font>

143
00:11:28,039 --> 00:11:31,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Didn't you ask me to come here
to think of a plan?</b></font>

144
00:11:31,839 --> 00:11:34,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Haven't you settled it with Shancai yet?</b></font>

145
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:44,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There are some things
that you don't understand.</b></font>

146
00:11:44,959 --> 00:11:45,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then ask me.</b></font>

147
00:11:46,439 --> 00:11:48,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Leave your girl problems
to the love expert.</b></font>

148
00:11:49,799 --> 00:11:51,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Mr. Love Expert,</b></font>

149
00:11:52,359 --> 00:11:53,879
<font color="#ffff00"><b>let's hear what you have to say.</b></font>

150
00:11:56,919 --> 00:11:57,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Women.</b></font>

151
00:11:58,999 --> 00:12:00,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you think of them
as a musical instrument,</b></font>

152
00:12:01,559 --> 00:12:02,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>she's a violin.</b></font>

153
00:12:04,039 --> 00:12:07,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You have to accurately control
your strength, position, and tone</b></font>

154
00:12:08,559 --> 00:12:11,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>in order to play the best music.</b></font>

155
00:12:11,799 --> 00:12:13,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So what do you think?</b></font>

156
00:12:16,759 --> 00:12:17,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Master Ximen.</b></font>

157
00:12:17,959 --> 00:12:20,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even I didn't quite understand it,
let alone Si.</b></font>

158
00:12:20,919 --> 00:12:21,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Right?</b></font>

159
00:12:25,479 --> 00:12:26,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where's Si?</b></font>

160
00:12:37,679 --> 00:12:38,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you doing?</b></font>

161
00:12:40,919 --> 00:12:42,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you here?</b></font>

162
00:12:44,479 --> 00:12:45,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well...</b></font>

163
00:12:45,839 --> 00:12:47,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I have something to tell you.</b></font>

164
00:12:49,839 --> 00:12:51,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What is it?</b></font>

165
00:12:55,759 --> 00:12:57,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's not convenient here.
Let's go to the rooftop.</b></font>

166
00:13:07,319 --> 00:13:09,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I can easily do other things.</i></b></font>

167
00:13:10,079 --> 00:13:12,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>But why is love so hard?</i></b></font>

168
00:13:16,079 --> 00:13:17,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you want to say to me?</b></font>

169
00:13:18,919 --> 00:13:19,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Tell me.</b></font>

170
00:13:20,719 --> 00:13:22,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm starving.</b></font>

171
00:13:22,759 --> 00:13:26,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I should tell him openly.
I have to tell him how I really feel.</i></b></font>

172
00:13:26,439 --> 00:13:28,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I want to officially
be together with Daoming Si.</i></b></font>

173
00:13:34,439 --> 00:13:35,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well...</b></font>

174
00:13:37,799 --> 00:13:39,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's...</b></font>

175
00:13:47,679 --> 00:13:48,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I...</b></font>

176
00:13:49,359 --> 00:13:52,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Goodness. I must tell him
that I really like him.</i></b></font>

177
00:13:53,279 --> 00:13:55,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Or else we can't officially be together.</i></b></font>

178
00:13:57,839 --> 00:13:59,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What is it? Say what you want to say.</b></font>

179
00:14:00,719 --> 00:14:02,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're so fierce.</b></font>

180
00:14:02,399 --> 00:14:03,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Never mind.</b></font>

181
00:14:03,879 --> 00:14:06,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you mean? Are you playing with me?</b></font>

182
00:14:07,039 --> 00:14:08,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not.</b></font>

183
00:14:08,719 --> 00:14:10,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Your voice is too loud.</b></font>

184
