203
00:15:31,879 --> 00:15:33,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I see.</b></font>

204
00:15:41,999 --> 00:15:43,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Never mind. Don't force yourself.</b></font>

205
00:15:44,039 --> 00:15:47,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I know you're used to food
