<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

208
00:16:11,519 --> 00:16:15,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I thought you'd start dating Xiaozi.</b></font>

209
00:16:16,519 --> 00:16:17,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaozi?</b></font>

210
00:16:17,959 --> 00:16:18,879
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

211
00:16:19,919 --> 00:16:20,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Last time,</b></font>

212
00:16:21,479 --> 00:16:24,999
