233
00:17:47,879 --> 00:17:48,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>However,</b></font>

234
00:17:49,799 --> 00:17:51,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>if your mom finds out,</b></font>

235
00:17:52,479 --> 00:17:54,239
