237
00:18:00,559 --> 00:18:01,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've had enough.</b></font>

238
00:18:02,839 --> 00:18:04,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've decided not to contact you.</b></font>

239
00:18:08,359 --> 00:18:09,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I can't accept it.</b></font>

240
00:18:09,839 --> 00:18:12,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're leaving me
