<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's nonsense!</b></font>

242
00:18:17,399 --> 00:18:19,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't want to go through that again.</b></font>

243
00:18:25,279 --> 00:18:26,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've already made up my mind.</b></font>

244
00:18:27,919 --> 00:18:30,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>For you, even if I have
