00:19:14,839 --> 00:19:16,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She thinks too much.</b></font>

258
00:19:17,599 --> 00:19:18,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's right.</b></font>

259
00:19:18,639 --> 00:19:21,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>They're dating
