260
00:19:25,199 --> 00:19:26,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What is it? Do you have any ideas?</b></font>

261
00:19:29,559 --> 00:19:31,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's do what Lei couldn't do.</b></font>

262
00:19:32,119 --> 00:19:33,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's lend Si a helping hand.</b></font>

263
00:19:34,279 --> 00:19:35,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course.</b></font>

264
00:19:42,479 --> 00:19:43,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Wait.</b></font>

265
00:19:44,599 --> 00:19:45,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Someone will see us.</b></font>

266
00:19:46,119 --> 00:19:47,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's no one here.</b></font>

267
