<font color="#ffff00"><b>There is.</b></font>

268
00:19:50,559 --> 00:19:51,879
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Near the back. Somebody's there.</b></font>

269
00:19:53,039 --> 00:19:55,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you part of the Terracotta Army?
Where were you unearthed?</b></font>

270
00:19:55,759 --> 00:19:57,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're the Terracotta Army.</b></font>

271
00:19:57,439 --> 00:19:59,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aren't we already dating?</b></font>

272
00:19:59,799 --> 00:20:00,839
