<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you don't tell me,</b></font>

276
00:20:08,239 --> 00:20:09,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not letting you go.</b></font>

277
00:20:11,959 --> 00:20:13,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because...</b></font>

278
00:20:16,239 --> 00:20:18,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because my heart's beating so fast.
Because I'm too excited.</b></font>

279
00:20:18,759 --> 00:20:20,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because you're all I think about.</b></font>

280
00:20:20,399 --> 00:20:22,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because you're here in front of me.</b></font>

281
00:20:22,479 --> 00:20:24,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I can't breathe. So, no.</b></font>

282
00:20:25,039 --> 00:20:26,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you talking like that?</b></font>

283
00:20:28,479 --> 00:20:30,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's how I speak. So what?</b></font>

284
00:20:31,919 --> 00:20:34,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hearing you say those things
make me want to...</b></font>

285
00:20:36,399 --> 00:20:37,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>To...</b></font>

286
00:20:37,759 --> 00:20:40,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>So this is how it feels to be in love.</i></b></font>

287
00:20:40,839 --> 00:20:42,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>It's so unbelievable.</i></b></font>

288
00:20:42,879 --> 00:20:46,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>My feelings are overflowing
like a dam on the verge of bursting.</i></b></font>

289
00:20:52,679 --> 00:20:53,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaoyou.</b></font>

290
00:20:55,159 --> 00:20:57,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Move these inside.
-Sure. Right away.</b></font>

291
00:21:00,479 --> 00:21:02,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>TALENT'S TEA SHOP</b></font>

292
00:21:21,079 --> 00:21:22,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ximen?</b></font>

293
00:21:23,879 --> 00:21:26,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You should ask Shancai to do these things.</b></font>

294
00:21:27,319 --> 00:21:28,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She's stronger than you.</b></font>

295
00:21:29,959 --> 00:21:31,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you here?</b></font>

296
00:21:31,679 --> 00:21:35,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you here to buy milk tea or...</b></font>

297
00:21:35,159 --> 00:21:36,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I came for you.</b></font>

298
00:21:37,199 --> 00:21:38,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Me?</b></font>

299
00:21:39,079 --> 00:21:40,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why?</b></font>

300
00:21:40,879 --> 00:21:43,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I'm a bit busy now.</b></font>

301
00:21:43,639 --> 00:21:44,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's fine.</b></font>

302
00:21:45,239 --> 00:21:46,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I can wait for you.</b></font>

303
00:21:47,519 --> 00:21:49,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaoyou, are the ten orders
of White Jasmine Dew</b></font>

304
00:21:49,599 --> 00:21:51,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and 15 orders of Peach Red Royale done?</b></font>

305
00:21:51,279 --> 00:21:52,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The customer will be here soon.</b></font>

306
00:21:53,319 --> 00:21:54,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Right away.</b></font>

307
00:21:55,399 --> 00:21:59,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aren't you the guy who helped
with our sales the last time?</b></font>

308
00:21:59,439 --> 00:22:02,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Sorry for disturbing you.
-How could that be? Thank you.</b></font>

309
00:22:02,599 --> 00:22:04,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Are you here for Xiaoyou?
-Yes.</b></font>

310
00:22:05,359 --> 00:22:07,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She still needs to work for another hour.</b></font>

311
00:22:07,559 --> 00:22:09,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's fine. I can wait for her.</b></font>

312
00:22:09,559 --> 00:22:10,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's okay.</b></font>

313
00:22:10,799 --> 00:22:12,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaoyou, leave earlier today.</b></font>

314
00:22:13,079 --> 00:22:14,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll take care of this.</b></font>

