00:22:14,959 --> 00:22:15,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Can I do that?</b></font>

316
00:22:16,479 --> 00:22:17,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't let him wait. You can go.</b></font>

317
00:22:19,879 --> 00:22:22,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Thank you, ma'am.
-You're welcome.</b></font>

318
00:22:49,239 --> 00:22:51,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Am I mistaken?</i></b></font>

319
00:23:18,599 --> 00:23:21,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Who are they? Why are they following me?</i></b></font>

320
00:23:28,799 --> 00:23:29,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai.</b></font>

321
00:23:32,199 --> 00:23:33,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you all right?</b></font>

322
00:23:33,839 --> 00:23:35,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who were you hiding from?</b></font>

323
00:23:36,039 --> 00:23:38,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've been followed by strange guys.</b></font>

324
00:23:40,279 --> 00:23:41,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come, this way.</b></font>

325
00:23:57,159 --> 00:23:57,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come here.</b></font>

326
00:24:09,399 --> 00:24:10,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come here.</b></font>

327
00:24:20,559 --> 00:24:22,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>They're obviously Si's bodyguards.</b></font>

328
00:24:26,879 --> 00:24:29,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you plan to do?
