329
00:24:33,959 --> 00:24:35,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I should.</b></font>

330
00:24:36,479 --> 00:24:37,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>However,</b></font>

331
00:24:38,679 --> 00:24:40,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-I'm worried--
