332
00:24:40,519 --> 00:24:41,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>would fight with his mom.</b></font>

333
00:24:42,519 --> 00:24:43,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Right?</b></font>

334
00:24:44,719 --> 00:24:45,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

335
