<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then let's not tell Si for now.</b></font>

336
00:24:55,999 --> 00:24:58,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si loses all reason when it comes to you.</b></font>

337
00:25:01,799 --> 00:25:03,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ximen and I are also afraid
