338
00:25:04,199 --> 00:25:05,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It might worsen the situation.</b></font>

339
00:25:12,479 --> 00:25:14,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not sure what to do anymore.</b></font>

340
00:25:16,199 --> 00:25:17,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Well,</b></font>

341
00:25:18,039 --> 00:25:19,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think you'd be fine for now.</b></font>

342
00:25:20,119 --> 00:25:21,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b>However,</b></font>

343
00:25:21,879 --> 00:25:23,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>try not to go home first.</b></font>

344
00:25:25,279 --> 00:25:27,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>They'll surely be back.</b></font>

345
00:25:29,319 --> 00:25:30,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay.</b></font>

346
00:25:30,639 --> 00:25:32,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll stay with Xiaoyou for a while.</b></font>

347
00:25:36,079 --> 00:25:38,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>By the way, why are you in this area?</b></font>

348
00:25:42,799 --> 00:25:43,799
