<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who told you that?</b></font>

352
00:25:50,759 --> 00:25:51,879
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is it true?</b></font>

353
00:25:54,959 --> 00:25:57,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ximen told me earlier
