354
00:25:58,359 --> 00:25:59,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And they're tasting some tea together.</b></font>

355
00:26:00,719 --> 00:26:01,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Actually...</b></font>

356
00:26:04,719 --> 00:26:06,039
