00:26:40,239 --> 00:26:41,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Shancai, I'll talk to you later.</i></b></font>

368
00:26:41,919 --> 00:26:43,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey, I...</b></font>

369
00:26:46,159 --> 00:26:47,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Take me to Ximen's house.</b></font>

