371
00:27:10,119 --> 00:27:12,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why did you trick Shancai
into going to your house?</b></font>

372
00:27:15,559 --> 00:27:16,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's a surprise.</b></font>

373
00:27:18,879 --> 00:27:20,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's not something weird, right?</b></font>

374
00:27:21,519 --> 00:27:23,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaoyou, trust me.</b></font>

375
00:27:26,199 --> 00:27:29,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You won't harm Shancai. I trust you.</b></font>

376
00:27:37,319 --> 00:27:39,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You seem to be in a good mood.</b></font>

377
00:27:41,319 --> 00:27:42,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

378
00:27:42,399 --> 00:27:43,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I have to keep moving forward.</b></font>

379
00:27:46,399 --> 00:27:48,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. I'll tell you the truth.</b></font>

380
00:27:50,159 --> 00:27:52,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We're trying to help Shancai
and Si take their relationship</b></font>

381
00:27:52,639 --> 00:27:53,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>one step further.</b></font>

382
00:27:55,279 --> 00:27:56,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>One step further?</b></font>

383
00:27:57,559 --> 00:27:59,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I see.</b></font>

384
00:27:59,959 --> 00:28:02,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>However, if their relationship goes well,</b></font>

385
00:28:02,679 --> 00:28:04,319
<font color="#ffff00"><b>it's not good for your family, right?</b></font>

386
00:28:08,959 --> 00:28:10,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You should be worried.</b></font>

387
00:28:10,999 --> 00:28:12,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No, it's not like that.</b></font>

388
00:28:16,039 --> 00:28:17,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai...</b></font>

389
00:28:18,399 --> 00:28:21,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She doesn't tell me
what she thinks lately.</b></font>

390
00:28:23,439 --> 00:28:24,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Maybe she's just shy.</b></font>

391
00:28:25,399 --> 00:28:26,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No.</b></font>

392
00:28:27,359 --> 00:28:30,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She'd tell me everything before.</b></font>

393
00:28:30,879 --> 00:28:31,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But now,</b></font>

394
00:28:32,479 --> 00:28:34,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>she just handles everything alone.</b></font>

395
00:28:35,959 --> 00:28:37,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I can't help her.</b></font>

396
00:28:37,839 --> 00:28:39,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And I even need her to protect me.</b></font>

397
00:28:40,079 --> 00:28:41,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm such a lousy friend.</b></font>

398
00:28:47,919 --> 00:28:49,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I did a lot of thinking lately.</b></font>

399
00:28:49,919 --> 00:28:51,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I hope Shancai can be happy.</b></font>

400
00:28:52,639 --> 00:28:55,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Since she likes Daoming Si
and Daoming Si likes her too,</b></font>

401
00:28:56,799 --> 00:28:58,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>then I'll raise both hands in support.</b></font>

402
00:29:03,479 --> 00:29:06,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>However, your family might get affected.</b></font>

403
00:29:07,199 --> 00:29:08,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Doesn't that matter to you?</b></font>

404
00:29:10,279 --> 00:29:13,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm already an adult.
I can help with our family's expenses.</b></font>

405
00:29:14,199 --> 00:29:15,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And didn't you see it too?</b></font>

406
00:29:16,279 --> 00:29:19,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai was not at the milk tea shop.
But I could handle it by myself.</b></font>

407
00:29:20,079 --> 00:29:23,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I believe our family can work together
and overcome any challenge.</b></font>

408
00:29:24,999 --> 00:29:26,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Didn't Shancai do the same?</b></font>

409
00:29:27,039 --> 00:29:28,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If she can do it, so can I.</b></font>

410
00:29:29,439 --> 00:29:30,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There's nothing I can't do.</b></font>

411
00:29:34,519 --> 00:29:37,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're not the Xiaoyou
who used to cry on the street anymore.</b></font>

412
00:29:38,679 --> 00:29:40,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You've grown up and become stronger.</b></font>

413
00:29:46,479 --> 00:29:48,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The one who made me strong</b></font>

414
00:29:49,319 --> 00:29:50,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>was you.</b></font>

415
00:29:54,519 --> 00:29:55,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>After what happened,</b></font>

416
00:29:56,039 --> 00:29:57,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I told myself I should change.</b></font>

417
00:29:59,519 --> 00:30:02,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You told me I should never
look down on myself.</b></font>

418
00:30:05,919 --> 00:30:07,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is that so? What an honor.</b></font>

419
00:30:08,879 --> 00:30:11,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You have to find a nice guy
to be your boyfriend in the future.</b></font>

420
00:30:12,119 --> 00:30:12,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Keep it up.</b></font>

421
00:30:20,519 --> 00:30:21,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ximen.</b></font>

422
00:30:23,239 --> 00:30:24,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you here?</b></font>

423
00:30:25,039 --> 00:30:28,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I walked past and thought
it was just someone who looked like you.</b></font>

424
00:30:28,479 --> 00:30:29,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Turns out it's really you.</b></font>

425
00:30:33,519 --> 00:30:35,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you on a date?</b></font>

426
00:30:35,639 --> 00:30:37,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Am I interrupting?</b></font>

427
00:30:38,599 --> 00:30:39,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No.</b></font>

428
00:30:40,199 --> 00:30:41,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're not.</b></font>

429
00:30:42,439 --> 00:30:45,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>By the way,
thanks for agreeing about Shancai.</b></font>

430
00:30:45,799 --> 00:30:48,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Also, we'll do our best
to help your family.</b></font>

431
00:30:49,199 --> 00:30:50,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You don't have to worry.</b></font>

432
00:30:51,639 --> 00:30:54,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Does she want to have a drink with us?</b></font>

433
00:30:56,399 --> 00:30:57,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No. She's not coming.</b></font>

434
00:30:58,119 --> 00:31:00,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Let's go.
-Bye.</b></font>

435
00:31:15,639 --> 00:31:17,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where's Xiaoyou?</b></font>

436
00:31:17,159 --> 00:31:18,879
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Wait! Why are you so impatient?</b></font>

437
00:31:18,959 --> 00:31:20,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I might be too late!</b></font>

438
00:31:20,799 --> 00:31:22,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're going to break my hand.</b></font>

439
00:31:22,759 --> 00:31:24,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Tell me where Ximen and Xiaoyou are.</b></font>

440
00:31:25,199 --> 00:31:26,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Master bedroom. Second door on the left.</b></font>

441
00:31:31,839 --> 00:31:33,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Does she think she's Xiaoyou's guardian?</b></font>

442
00:31:34,839 --> 00:31:35,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She's so easily tricked.</b></font>

443
00:31:37,559 --> 00:31:38,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaoyou.</b></font>

444
00:31:41,839 --> 00:31:42,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaoyou.</b></font>

445
00:31:44,359 --> 00:31:45,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you inside?</b></font>

446
00:31:51,679 --> 00:31:52,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaoyou.</b></font>

447
00:32:29,639 --> 00:32:30,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey.</b></font>

448
00:32:31,039 --> 00:32:32,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Are they trying to destroy my house?</i></b></font>

449
00:32:35,799 --> 00:32:36,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're at a bar?</b></font>

450
00:32:38,159 --> 00:32:42,559
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Didn't we agree to meet at your house
with Xiaoyou afterward?</i></b></font>

451
00:32:43,439 --> 00:32:45,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si and Shancai will be
locked in all night.</b></font>

452
00:32:46,039 --> 00:32:47,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's the point of being there?</b></font>

453
00:32:48,999 --> 00:32:51,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>We'll suffer if we wait
by their door all night.</i></b></font>

454
00:32:51,999 --> 00:32:52,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Makes sense.</b></font>

455
00:32:53,519 --> 00:32:54,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then I'll join you.</b></font>

456
00:32:55,799 --> 00:32:57,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come over.
You're the only one missing here.</b></font>

457
00:32:59,159 --> 00:33:00,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Okay. I'll head there now.</b></font>

458
00:33:09,599 --> 00:33:10,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Daoming Si?</b></font>

459
00:33:27,399 --> 00:33:28,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's going on?</b></font>

460
00:33:28,879 --> 00:33:30,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ximen and Meizuo kidnapped me.</b></font>

461
00:33:30,799 --> 00:33:31,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did you see Xiaoyou?</b></font>

462
00:33:32,519 --> 00:33:33,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No.</b></font>

463
00:33:35,279 --> 00:33:36,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Did I go into the wrong room?</b></font>

464
00:33:37,959 --> 00:33:39,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Those guys.</b></font>

465
00:33:44,559 --> 00:33:45,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey!</b></font>

466
00:33:46,119 --> 00:33:47,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Open up! Ximen, Meizuo.</b></font>

467
00:33:48,439 --> 00:33:50,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where did you take Xiaoyou?</b></font>

468
00:33:50,639 --> 00:33:51,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Hey!</b></font>

469
00:33:51,679 --> 00:33:53,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Stop screaming.
-Open the door!</b></font>

470
00:33:53,359 --> 00:33:54,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You've been tricked.</b></font>

471
00:33:58,679 --> 00:33:59,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you mean?</b></font>

472
00:34:02,359 --> 00:34:04,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I received a call from Xiaoyou.</b></font>

473
00:34:04,559 --> 00:34:06,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-She said she's here--
-So you've been tricked.</b></font>

474
00:34:11,399 --> 00:34:12,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You mean...</b></font>

475
00:34:13,239 --> 00:34:16,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Xiaoyou worked with Ximen
and Meizuo to trick me?</b></font>

476
00:34:16,959 --> 00:34:18,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>They planned this?</b></font>

477
00:34:25,559 --> 00:34:27,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No. I have to find a way out.</b></font>

478
00:34:27,119 --> 00:34:28,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That door's the only way out.</b></font>

479
00:34:29,999 --> 00:34:32,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-But it's locked.
-So we can't go out.</b></font>

480
00:34:32,759 --> 00:34:33,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So what do we do?</b></font>

481
00:34:35,079 --> 00:34:37,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't care. I'm with you anyway.</b></font>

482
00:34:37,719 --> 00:34:39,879
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Be serious. Think of something, okay?</b></font>

483
00:34:39,959 --> 00:34:42,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even if I can think of something,
I'm not going out.</b></font>

484
00:34:45,999 --> 00:34:48,679
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Those guys. They should've just told me.</b></font>

485
00:34:48,999 --> 00:34:50,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No need to tie me up like that.</b></font>

486
00:34:52,759 --> 00:34:53,759
<font color="#ffff00"><b>In that case,</b></font>

487
00:34:55,999 --> 00:34:58,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>sorry, I'll tie you back up.</b></font>

488
00:34:58,959 --> 00:35:00,119
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you crazy?</b></font>

489
00:35:07,239 --> 00:35:09,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not ready yet.</b></font>

490
00:35:11,039 --> 00:35:13,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If I give you time to get ready,
you'll surely run away again.</b></font>

491
00:35:15,159 --> 00:35:16,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>He saw through me.</i></b></font>

492
00:35:32,719 --> 00:35:33,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You might not know yet,</b></font>

493
00:35:34,919 --> 00:35:36,079
<font color="#ffff00"><b>but this expression of yours</b></font>

494
00:35:36,759 --> 00:35:37,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>fascinates me the most.</b></font>

495
00:36:30,279 --> 00:36:31,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai.</b></font>

496
00:36:32,239 --> 00:36:33,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're so short.</b></font>

497
00:36:33,839 --> 00:36:35,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b>My neck's about to break.</b></font>

498
00:36:36,559 --> 00:36:38,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Who told you to be tall like a giraffe?</b></font>

499
00:36:41,239 --> 00:36:44,399
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Make yourself taller for me, okay?</b></font>

500
00:36:46,199 --> 00:36:47,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm so nervous already.</b></font>

501
00:36:48,079 --> 00:36:49,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How can I do that?</b></font>

502
00:36:50,519 --> 00:36:52,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's there to be nervous about?</b></font>

503
00:36:52,719 --> 00:36:53,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Your face is so red.</b></font>

504
00:36:54,959 --> 00:36:56,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It might be contagious.</b></font>

505
00:37:08,199 --> 00:37:10,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>It looks like things might not go smoothly</i></b></font>

506
00:37:10,959 --> 00:37:13,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>even if we're together already.</i></b></font>

507
00:37:14,279 --> 00:37:18,639
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Especially since our situation
is not ordinary at all.</i></b></font>

508
00:37:31,679 --> 00:37:36,039
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you think this room
is like that wooden mansion in Canada?</b></font>

509
00:37:43,799 --> 00:37:44,959
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes. Canada.</b></font>

510
00:37:46,479 --> 00:37:47,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>At the time,</b></font>

511
00:37:48,199 --> 00:37:52,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I thought Xiaoyou went out
to see the night view in the snowstorm.</b></font>

512
00:37:57,239 --> 00:38:00,279
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So I went out to find her.
Then I got lost.</b></font>

513
00:38:00,959 --> 00:38:02,719
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I almost got eaten by wolves.</b></font>

514
00:38:05,599 --> 00:38:06,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It was so scary.</b></font>

515
00:38:25,639 --> 00:38:28,159
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Then you...
-Then what did I do?</b></font>

516
00:38:33,279 --> 00:38:34,839
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I became your savior.</b></font>

517
00:38:35,679 --> 00:38:36,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Right?</b></font>

518
00:38:43,439 --> 00:38:45,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You always got yourself involved
and saved me.</b></font>

519
00:38:46,479 --> 00:38:48,439
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you mean I got myself involved?</b></font>

520
00:38:52,759 --> 00:38:54,359
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What I'm trying to say is</b></font>

521
00:38:56,919 --> 00:38:58,519
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've always been grateful.</b></font>

522
00:39:02,119 --> 00:39:04,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No matter how many times it is,
I'd go and save you.</b></font>

523
00:39:11,879 --> 00:39:13,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because I really love you.</b></font>

524
00:39:14,439 --> 00:39:15,479
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I can't live without you.</b></font>

525
00:39:25,039 --> 00:39:26,999
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why do you have that expression again?</b></font>

526
00:39:27,119 --> 00:39:28,239
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I might...</b></font>

527
00:39:30,919 --> 00:39:33,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Happiness like this is like standing</i></b></font>

528
00:39:34,399 --> 00:39:36,199
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>on a piece of floating ice in the sea.</i></b></font>

529
00:39:36,759 --> 00:39:39,919
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>It might melt anytime.</i></b></font>

530
00:39:53,839 --> 00:39:56,599
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ma'am, the investigative report
from Shanghai is here.</b></font>

531
00:39:58,519 --> 00:39:59,799
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let me see it.</b></font>

